  <programme start="20251226110000 +0000" stop="20251226120000 +0000" channel="Bravo.ca">
    <title>The Real Housewives of Vancouver</title>
    <desc>In keeping with the original style set by its popular American Bravo predecessors, this Canadian version of the &quot;Real Housewives&quot; franchise follows a handful of Vancouver&#x27;s wealthiest and most elite women -- not all of whom begin filming as wives -- with a focus on the relationships and often outrageous drama that fill their lives. The five featured women include Reiko MacKenzie, whose hobbies include studying martial arts and collecting exotic sports cars; Christina Kiesel, who has been divorced twice and is now content enough to &quot;play the field&quot; and travel the world; Ronnie Seterdahl Negus, a wife of 10 years who prides herself on her charity work; Jody Claman, a successful businesswoman whose ventures include a catering company and a high-end luxury boutique; and Mary Zilba, a divorcee and successful singer who put her career on hold to raise her three sons.</desc>
  </programme>
