  </programme>
  <programme start="20251223170000 +0000" stop="20251223173000 +0000" channel="SPEEDVISION.us">
    <title>What&#x27;s In the Barn?</title>
    <desc>S2 E6 Wounded Warrior Project
Home Depot Senior Vice President, Gordon Erickson, is a huge fan of Wheels Through Time. He is also a huge supporter of the Wounded Warrior program. For years the hardware giant has been donating goods and services to help returning servicemen with their fix-it-up projects. Now they would like to go one step further and build a WWII military bike to raise awareness and funds. Only problem is where to get one? Enter Dale and an exhaustive, time sensitive, cross country search for a rare military machine.</desc>
  </programme>
  <programme start="20251223173000 +0000" stop="20251223180000 +0000" channel="SPEEDVISION.us">
