    <title>What&#x27;s In the Barn?</title>
    <desc>S2 E5 Second Time&#x27;s a Charm
The RM Auction Company has worked with Dale before as a buyer, seller, historian, and caretaker at the prestigious Lee Hartung auction. But this event is no last minute rush to define one man’s treasures. This is a well calculated, time consuming, multi-media, and multi motorcycle and prized art deal.</desc>
  </programme>
  <programme start="20251224005900 +0000" stop="20251224012900 +0000" channel="SPEEDVISION.us">
    <title>What&#x27;s In the Barn?</title>
    <desc>S2 E6 Wounded Warrior Project
