    <desc>The Chiefs and Broncos end the Christmas Day slate with an AFC West matchup. Denver has won three of the last four meetings after a 22-19 decision in Week 11. Cornerback Ja&#x27;Quan McMillian (DEN) recorded two sacks and an interception in that victory.</desc>
  </programme>
  <programme start="20251226200000 +0000" stop="20251226230000 +0000" channel="NFLNetwork.us">
    <title>NFL Football : Dallas Cowboys at Washington Commanders</title>
    <desc>A Christmas Day tripleheader kicks off in the capital as the Commanders host the Cowboys. Dallas seeks a season sweep after doubling up Washington 44-22 in Week 7. Dak Prescott tossed three TD passes for Dallas, one a 74-yard strike to CeeDee Lamb.</desc>
  </programme>
