    <title>NFL Football : Detroit Lions at Minnesota Vikings</title>
    <desc>The Lions and Vikings deck the halls with this Christmas Day matchup from the North Star State. Minnesota snapped a five-game series slide with a 27-24 win at Detroit in Week 9. Quarterback J.J. McCarthy may be out of this game due to an injury.</desc>
