    <desc>For multiple drivers heading into the 2025 Indy 500, this is the moment they&#x27;ve been waiting 365 days for. Everyone behind the wheel is looking to fight off past ghosts. After a second place finish in &#x27;22 and &#x27;24, can O Ward finally kiss the bricks? Is it time for Dixon to get his second victory after nearly two decades? Will Larson pull off the double after the weather derailed him a year ago? There have never been more questions looking to be answered at the Indianapolis 500.</desc>
